<level type="section">
  <num>2-381.22</num>
  <heading>Electronic procurement.</heading>
  <level>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>The CPO may issue a solicitation by any electronic medium, including the Internet, electronic mail, or disk medium.</text>
  </level>
  <level>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>The CPO may accept responses to solicitations by any electronic medium, including the Internet, electronic mail, or disk medium.</text>
  </level>
